# Couette flow: linear velocity profile
# Validation: ux(y) = u_wall * y / Ly

Simulation couette D2Q9
Domain  L = 0.125 x 1.0  N = 4 x 32

Define u_wall = 0.05

Physics nu = 0.1

Boundary x periodic
Boundary south wall
Boundary north velocity(ux = u_wall, uy = 0)

Run 10000 steps
Output vtk every 2000 [rho, ux, uy]
